#
# Crontab addition for Duplicacy Scripts
#

# Minute, Hour, DoM, Month, DoW

# Backups every four hours
#Min Hour DoM Mon DoW  Command
#25   */4  *   *   *    __BIN__/cron-backup
25   *  *   *   *    __BIN__/cron-backup


# Routine Maintenance
#Min Hour DoM Mon DoW  Command
0    1    *   *   *    __BIN__/cron-daily
0    2    *   *   Sun  __BIN__/cron-weekly
0    3    1-7 *   Sun  __BIN__/cron-monthly
